{title: Chord Definition Copy}

{define: Am base-fret 1 frets x 0 2 2 1 0}
{define: Amin copy Am}
{define: A- copy Am}
{define: Cmaj7 base-fret 1 frets x 3 2 0 0 0}
{define: CM7 copy Cmaj7}

{start_of_verse}
[Am]Sometimes we use [Amin]different names
[A-]For the very [Am]same chord
[Cmaj7]Copy lets us [CM7]reuse definitions
[Am]Without repeating [Cmaj7]every fret
{end_of_verse}
